Package com.cafean.client.ui.tools

Class InsertMouseHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.client.ui.tools.MouseHandler
      • com.cafean.client.ui.tools.InsertMouseHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.event.MouseListener, java.awt.event.MouseMotionListener, java.util.EventListener
    public class InsertMouseHandler
extends MouseHandler
    The Insert Tool, a MouseHandler for insertion into a ZoomablePanel. Handles the creation and insertion of new components and the management of AbstractInsertHandler instances used to create and dimension various Insertable components.
    See Also:
    Insertable, AbstractInsertHandler
